{"tid":1175878,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"14歲富二代打機輸了 27刀斬死朋友","createTime":"2019-05-29T00:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T01:54:06.000Z","uid":3090,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"726b987097c2894eeb0c6917fde1f6e09ae72d9c","tid":1175878,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T00:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dVGdODB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdVGdODB.png&h=37bc242b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖爾達（左）27刀斬死波帕，其豪宅遺下一條血路。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭一名俄裔富二代與友打機輸了，一怒之下狂斬對方27刀，謀殺罪成被判監。<br />\n<br />\n14歲的圖爾達（Vasya Turda）獲從商的父親送贈電子遊戲機，邀15歲朋友波帕（Vasya Pop）到他的豪宅一起玩。圖爾達不敵波帕，不甘受辱，拿刀斬波帕，波帕頸部中刀，逃命時被圖爾達追斬，最後身中27刀死亡。<br />\n<br />\n波帕的頭幾乎被斬掉，屍體遭圖爾達虐待。案發現場遺下一條血路。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指圖爾達指被波帕騷擾和侮辱，曾在咖啡店有女孩在場情況下剝他的褲。<br />\n<br />\n不過，法官最後裁定圖爾達謀殺罪成，判監三年半。控方要求加刑15年。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"7ce4fd4f924e32ad525dd9cd5aa3416b9de5707f","tid":1175878,"uid":174191,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T00:28:43.000Z","msg":"俄裔 戰鬥民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b917f198946ddf475d8bd76c88156daa8c01e462","tid":1175878,"uid":76999,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T00:29:32.000Z","msg":"咩話 謀殺都係坐3年半<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78ff50ef79ea96e0cd5d57c94efb835ee6a8240","tid":1175878,"uid":36134,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T00:29:52.000Z","msg":"判得三年半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等睇死者老豆出手 俄佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c935e089962ebc5b3ae57551d3251412c6c238d","tid":1175878,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T00:31:48.000Z","msg":"窮人生仔正仆街，爸母又唔識教"},{"pid":"2aa22230a32f7a56814c8577d6a622e044e4fe9d","tid":1175878,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,